Cyberpunk style: A towering digital metropolis at night where two massive parallel data highways made of glowing code streams converge into a single unified pathway. One highway pulses with fading amber light representing legacy systems, while the other blazes with vibrant electric blue representing modern architecture. At the convergence point, intricate circuit patterns spiral outward like a technological mandala. Holographic server towers rise in the background, their surfaces etched with flowing data patterns. Neon reflections shimmer on rain-slicked surfaces below, while streams of binary particles flow through the air like digital fireflies. The atmosphere is dense with fog and the glow of countless connection points, suggesting a complex ecosystem of interconnected services finding harmony.
